pittsburgh is a 1942 american comedy film directed by frank mcdonald and written by dorrell mcgowan and stuart e. mcgowan . the film stars william boyd , andy clyde , rand brooks , william frawley , william frawley , william frawley , andy devine , william frawley , andy devine , william frawley , andy devine , william frawley , andy devine , william frawley , andy devine , william frawley , andy devine , william frawley , andy devine , william frawley , andy devine , charles ' pittsburgh ' drake , and the rest of the pittsburgh steelers . the film was released on may 21 , 1942 , by republic pictures .